summary: Being married to Sandor Clegane would include
title: Being married to Sandor Clegane would include
body:
( GIF Credit [ X ] )


- Him always feeling that he is not enough to you, his wife, not mattering if you are highborned or not, and you having to reasure sometimes that you love him not for who he is -meaning the Hound, or the visible head of House Clegane nowadays- but because who he is inside, the part of him that only you knows.

- Him being kind and even a bit cheesy on purpose when you two are alone, or at least trying it, because his kind actions are always a bit harsh -like when he wants to show you how much he loves you by embracing you and he ends almost suffocating you by his enormous stregth- or a bit awkward, even funny, when he try to say something beautiful to you and ends saying something he could say to a whore in a brothel.

- Him always being highly protective to you, even when he is phisically away from you, and appearing in the correct moment to save you from a falling from your horse, or to being hurted in the slightiest way by any other person.

- Him calling you “my bitch”, and laughing loudly because you don’t mind to be called that, as long as you have married a hound.

- Him loving to fuck you while you are on four, and going really hard, not mattering if you are agreeing about the posture or not on first, because he knows how to make you to like it.

- Him riding everywhere with you on his horse, because he hates to think that any other man could look at you lustfully in the streets if you ride by your own, and he knows that no one would dare to do that if you are in the same horse he is riding.

- Him, if you get pregnant soon, boasting of his masculinity levels, as well as of your high capacity of engender, and if any around jokes about the fact that you two are going to have a little pup, him crushing his fist on the face of the poor fool who dares to say that, even when deep inside he finds the idea funny.

- Him making you to sleep against his chest all time, not leaving you too many room to move, just because he wants to keep you safe and to make you feel loved even when you are sleeping.

summary: Reasons why sweet pea is a Targaryen
body:
Reasons why sweet pea is a Targaryen

  • Perfect hair
  • It isnt white
  • But that doesnt make it any less perfect
  • Connection to reptiles (serpents/dragons)
  • Threatened to burn down riverdale high during the riots (fire)
  • Likes to punch things (blood)
  • Southsider = outsider (like daenerys)
  • Speaking of that, he’s the moon of my life
  • Also, he looks good in black
  • Obsessed with justice for himself and his people
  • Gorgeous eyes
  • Not purple but still gorgeous
  • 10/10 would’ve wanted a dragon when he was a kid
  • Not the official king but a king in his own right (also like dany)
